[It should be stressed that the diagnosis is unconfirmed, and that a
previous case of suspected Ebola fever in Tanzania was not confirmed. The
Ebola fever outbreak appears to be still contained to the region of
northern Uganda around Gulu, apart from 2 so far minor escapes. - Mod.CP
